Class CartesianTimeSeriesAxis

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.configuration.Axis

  • public class CartesianTimeSeriesAxis
extends CartesianTimeAxis
    This object is used to map defined axis as time series. This is used to have time series charts.
